with the taste of <i>makgeolli</i>.

399
00:17:08,794 --> 00:17:09,795
Cheers.

400
00:17:09,862 --> 00:17:11,797
-Please try some.
-I've never had anything like this.

401
00:17:12,598 --> 00:17:14,033
It's really good.

402
00:17:14,099 --> 00:17:16,568
It's pretty strong too.

403
00:17:16,635 --> 00:17:18,771
