and when it turns into a soup.

421
00:17:56,542 --> 00:17:58,277
Do you like its texture?

422
00:17:58,343 --> 00:18:01,680
I like the part
between the tentacles and the trunk.

423
00:18:01,747 --> 00:18:03,248
It's the firmest part.

424
00:18:03,315 --> 00:18:04,683
-The center part?
-Yes.

425
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:07,286
-That's my favorite.
-It's like people who like pork cartilage.

426
00:18:07,352 --> 00:18:09,955
That's what people don't like,
yet that part is your favorite?

427
00:18:10,022 --> 00:18:11,457
If someone wants to throw that out,

428
00:18:11,523 --> 00:18:13,425
I want to pick it up

429
00:18:13,492 --> 00:18:15,994
