wash it, and cook it for myself.

430
00:18:16,061 --> 00:18:20,032
I see. He has a unique liking for texture.

431
00:18:20,099 --> 00:18:22,901
That was all for Jae-joong's fridge.

432
00:18:23,802 --> 00:18:26,405
He's a guy who loves Korean cuisine.

433
00:18:26,472 --> 00:18:31,810
