436
00:18:35,547 --> 00:18:37,783
Asia's spiciest.

437
00:18:37,850 --> 00:18:39,918
AS THEY EXPECTED,
HE WANTS SOMETHING SPICY

438
00:18:39,985 --> 00:18:41,386
You all expected this one, right?

439
00:18:41,453 --> 00:18:43,489
I've tried

440
00:18:43,555 --> 00:18:46,892
