441
00:18:46,959 --> 00:18:48,160
Wasn't it hard?

442
00:18:48,227 --> 00:18:49,595
It really was.

443
00:18:49,661 --> 00:18:50,963
But I want to be abused today.

444
00:18:51,029 --> 00:18:53,465
He wants to be abused.

445
00:18:53,532 --> 00:18:55,000
It's not for everyone, then.

446
00:18:55,067 --> 00:18:58,403
I have a question.
How spicy do you want it to be?

447
00:18:58,470 --> 00:18:59,872
I have to stick to my work ethic.

448
00:18:59,938 --> 00:19:01,707
Your work ethic?

449
00:19:03,408 --> 00:19:06,078
He thinks there's a limit to spiciness.

450
00:19:06,145 --> 00:19:08,614
I think it'd be great
if it makes my philtrum sweat

451
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:11,383
