452
00:19:11,450 --> 00:19:14,186
-Make his philtrum sweat.
-That's pretty spicy.

453
00:19:14,253 --> 00:19:17,523
Here's his second order.

454
00:19:17,589 --> 00:19:19,825
-Do You Know Makgeolli?
-Do You Know Makgeolli?

455
00:19:19,892 --> 00:19:22,027
Something I can pair with <i>makgeolli</i>.

456
00:19:22,094 --> 00:19:25,097
Something that'll go well with <i>makgeolli</i>.

457
00:19:25,164 --> 00:19:27,432
Let's decide on the contestants.

458
00:19:27,499 --> 00:19:29,001
This is an away game for those chefs,

459
00:19:29,067 --> 00:19:31,670
so we thought it might be a bit hard.

460
00:19:31,737 --> 00:19:35,574
So we'll give the top Asian chefs,
including Keun-suk,

461
00:19:35,641 --> 00:19:38,610
