1264
00:54:05,108 --> 00:54:07,744
-He's steaming the squid.
-The squid too?

1265
00:54:07,811 --> 00:54:09,913
He's steaming the squid.

1266
00:54:10,513 --> 00:54:14,417
Chef Hyun-suk is
pulling the crab pieces apart.

1267
00:54:14,484 --> 00:54:16,653
-Gosh.
-I think he's only using the meat.

1268
00:54:17,754 --> 00:54:19,222
-Enoki.
-Enoki mushroom.

1269
