1285
00:54:59,095 --> 00:55:01,364
I guess he's using it all for <i>sundae</i>.

1286
00:55:01,431 --> 00:55:04,968
-He used it to mince the shrimps.
-He did.

1287
00:55:05,035 --> 00:55:07,504
He'll fill the <i>sundae</i>
