-It's rice cake.

1298
00:55:34,464 --> 00:55:37,367
-It's rice cake.
-Did he boil it in <i>makgeolli</i>?

1299
00:55:37,434 --> 00:55:39,536
Gosh, the <i>makgeolli</i>. What a shame.

