1329
00:56:53,576 --> 00:56:54,844
This is what <i>Chef & My Fridge</i> is like.

1330
00:56:54,911 --> 00:56:57,614
We even make the 37th place anxious.

1331
00:56:59,249 --> 00:57:00,650
Darn it.

1332
00:57:00,717 --> 00:57:02,352
I don't have enough time.

1333
00:57:02,919 --> 00:57:05,054
-He got more pork belly.
-He just flattened those,

1334
00:57:05,121 --> 00:57:08,425
