1350
00:57:46,429 --> 00:57:48,798
I think he should use the one-minute stop.

1351
00:57:48,865 --> 00:57:49,899
Right now?

1352
00:57:49,966 --> 00:57:51,901
-That'll be bad.
-Wait, aren't you…

1353
00:57:51,968 --> 00:57:55,605
