-Yes.

1367
00:58:25,368 --> 00:58:26,703
-Fish sauce.
-Anchovy sauce.

1368
00:58:26,769 --> 00:58:27,937
-Anchovy sauce.
-Yes.

1369
00:58:28,004 --> 00:58:32,041
