00:59:46,349 --> 00:59:47,850
HE GETS A BUSHEL
FOR A PECK OF SALT

1398
00:59:48,418 --> 00:59:49,652
IT'S SO MUCH FUN TO WATCH

1399
00:59:50,219 --> 00:59:51,521
GOT MY REVENGE

1400
00:59:51,588 --> 00:59:53,590
