1405
01:00:02,465 --> 01:00:04,233
-You have to stay still.
-Hyun-suk, be quiet.

1406
01:00:04,300 --> 01:00:05,301
You got this!

1407
01:00:05,368 --> 01:00:07,203
-Do not move, Hyun-suk.
-You can do it!

1408
