DESPITE HIS ATTACK

1411
01:00:13,343 --> 01:00:15,511
-Soju.
-He's using soju too.

1412
01:00:15,578 --> 01:00:17,180
-He used soju.
-He put soju inside.

1413
01:00:17,246 --> 01:00:18,848
