-You got this!

1418
01:00:28,891 --> 01:00:31,661
-You got this! You can do it!
-Ten seconds.

1419
01:00:31,728 --> 01:00:33,696
-Vamos.
-You can do it!

1420
01:00:33,763 --> 01:00:35,431
Seven. Six.

1421
01:00:35,498 --> 01:00:36,766
-Five.
-Five seconds, Hyun-suk.

1422
01:00:37,667 --> 01:00:40,336
-Three. Two. One.
-Three. Two. One.

1423
01:00:40,403 --> 01:00:42,972
You can begin now, Hyun-suk.

1424
01:00:43,039 --> 01:00:46,776
